The paper discusses a new computing paradigm inspired by the operation of the brain, which suggests a connection to neural networks and artificial intelligence (cs.NE). The proposed architecture is based on memcapacitive systems, which are related to electronic circuits and devices (cs.AR). The paper also discusses energy expenditures, which suggests a connection to energy-efficient computing (cs.EM) and emerging technologies (cs.ET). Finally, the paper proposes a new type of memory, which suggests a connection to memory systems and technology (cs.ETL).
